title: All Current Warhammer 40K Codecies 07-01-2013
description:

-2005 - 4th Edition Black Templars
-2008 - 4th Edition Orks
-2008 - 5th Edition Space Marines
-2009 - 5th Edition Imperial Guard
-2009 - 5th Edition Space Wolves
-2010 - 5th Edition Blood Angels
-2010 - 5th Edition Dark Eldar
-2010 - 5th Edition Tyranids
-2011 - 5th Edition Grey Knights
-2011 - 5th Edition Necrons
-2011 - 5th Edition Sisters of Battle (part 1)
-2011 - 5th Edition Sisters of Battle (part 2)
-2012 - 6th Edition Chaos Space Marines
-2013 - 6th Edition Chaos Daemons
-2013 - 6th Edition Dark Angels
-2013 - 6th Edition Eldar (Iyanden)
-2013 - 6th Edition Eldar
-2013 - 6th Edition Tau Empire
